Routes → Wrapper for all route definitions; decides which page to render based on the URL.

Route → Defines a specific path and the component to display for that path.

ToastContainer → Displays toast notifications triggered anywhere in the app.

Alternative Ways if Token is Not in Header
Option 1: Store Token in Cookies
Store token as an HTTP-only cookie on login.
The browser will automatically send it with every request.

Option 2: Store in Local Storage & Add Interceptor
Save token in localStorage.
Use Axios interceptor to attach it automatically to every request: